This is how to add of lst:
   Remember that result is item 1 in lst
   Remember that i is 3
   Do this quotient of (diff of lst's length and 2) and 2 times:
      Remember that x is item i in lst
      When x is more than result, then:
         Remember that result is x
      End when
      Remember that i is sum of i and 2
   End do
   The answer is result
